<br>
&quot;Its time to play, little ants!!! Time to play with your Uncle Mad!!!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 157<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/13/01 8:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://lizazz.tripod.com/valmad6.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The approach</span><hr size=1> Madmartigan started to walk slowly to the village. People stopped what they were doing to look at this person who had glowing eyes and a sword in his hand. Then, one by one they began to realize his intentions. Calls from all around the village were for the guards to come. A long row of 20 guards came and stood in Madmartigans way to the village. The commander stepped forwards and spoke.<br>
<br>
&quot;We know what you came here to do!! And we will not let you. Men, ready weapons!!&quot;<br>
<br>
Madmartigan smerked as the order was given out. He looked at the man in front of him. &quot;So you want to play,&quot; He said, &quot;lets play.&quot;<br>
<br>
In the blink of an eye, Madmartigan brought up his sword and had sliced off the man's head. He looked to the row of what was now 19 guards, they were now heasitant and starting to fall back. Mad locked his eyes on one and pointed, &quot;You,&quot; he whispered, &quot;Your next.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hypnos>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 160<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/13/01 10:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=C:\WINDOWS\Desktop\Stuff\hypnos.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The approach</span><hr size=1> ***In his cave at Lemnos, Hypnos looks into the river Lethe to see Madmartigan causing some problems in a village... His Siblings were doing there job, bringing madness, evil, and doom to the people of the world. It seemed that Lyssa was heading this &quot;attack&quot; on Madmartigan...*** <p>~*~*~*~*~Thè göd öƒ §|èèp~*~*~*~*~        </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 158<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/13/01 10:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://lizazz.tripod.com/valmad6.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The slaughter</span><hr size=1> Madmartigan lept at the man he had pointed to. He swung the sword downwards and sliced the man down his cheast, spilling out his intestines. Madmartigan turned the blade in its path to peirce the man next to him's heart, all this as fast as lightning. He saw attacks made on him and he blocked and parried them all, sliceing and stabbing inbetween. When it was all over, Madmartigan stood alone, his sword had hit every time he had swung. Twenty lives were lost, twenty bodies lay at Mad's feet, and he smiled. He looked up and saw the villagers running around, trying to get away.<br>
<br>
&quot;Come little ants, time to be squished.&quot;<br>
<br>
Mad raced into the village to quench is blood thirst. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 159<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/13/01 3:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://lizazz.tripod.com/valmad6.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A village destroyed</span><hr size=1> It was an hour later and Madmartigan surveyed the destroyed village. Everyone who had lived in the village was now dead or dieing. He walked back to where he came to the village, straw huts burining red around him. He smiled. He walked on people, the ones who were still alive groaned and cryed out as he crushed skulls, ribcages, and broke arms and legs in his wake. He had his fun, but what was this, one person was standing, and she was in his way. Quickley he walked up to her.<br>
<br>
&quot;Have you anything to say before i kill you too little ant?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Yes,&quot; Said the woman, &quot;You are a vile creature, and i shall kill you for what you have done.&quot;<br>
<br>
Madmartigan chukled as she spoke. &quot;Why thank you, your words are too kind.&quot;<br>
<br>
Madmartigan struck out with his hand and grasped her throat. &quot;I shall show you how vile i am.&quot; Madmartigan thrust his other hand out while the woman squirmed in his hand. His hand hit the center of her cheast and kept going. He dug his hand deep into her body, then he pulled it out, along with her heart. The woman looked at him in horror as she died, watching her heart beat its final times. and the man, who then took a bite out of it.<br>
<br>
Madmartigan droped the heart and the woman at the same time. Blood coated his whole body, and then he started to walk. Walked to somewhere elce, for the same reason that he had came to this village. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hypnos>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 163<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/13/01 3:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=C:\WINDOWS\Desktop\Stuff\hypnos.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A village destroyed</span><hr size=1> ***Looked in dismay at the village and its dead or dieing... Then disappears and reappears at the distroyed village wearing a black robe,a silver mask, and his goblet of sleeping potion. He walked arround the destroyed village bringing the souls of the dead to the underworld and letting the dieing drink from the cup of sleep to have a final slumber to lighten there pain... What a shame it was to let such a good warrior fall into such corruption. Looks at his sister as she glides behind Madmartigan without notice...*** &quot;Well family is family, but who knows maybe some good might come out of this...&quot;  <p>~*~*~*~*~Thè göd öƒ §|èèp~*~*~*~*~        </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 160<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/13/01 3:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsuni