Madmartigan's shell, now Dymastar, looked at Anya and grinned evily, &quot;And his body contains awesome powers that i now command!!! I think that whoever you think can stop me will die in vane. Bring this person out!!!! Who do you think can stop the awesome DYMASTAR?!!!!!!!!!!!&quot;<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usheyala.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sheyala</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 259<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/16/01 4:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://geocities.com/Tokyo/Pagoda/8446/mononoke_poster.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Laughter in the face of insanity</span><hr size=1> ::Anya again smirked in her way.  The tooth filled mouth looked dangerous even then, but most ahd gotten used to it by then..  She stood to her full height her head fully erect the smirk turning nto a grin and so on::<br>
<br>
&gt;<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START >D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/grin.gif ALT=">D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ymaster is it? heh heh heh heh that little pixie I stepped on so many years back?  Hmm should have left you to drown in my footprint little one.  And funny you talk to me as if I have been forgotten by my own people.  No, it is not I that will stand in your way.  Not now.  Mayhaps not later.  You are not a threat to me or to my home, but one woman will beat you Dymaster.  Your arrogance will be your downfall.  it always was.&lt;&lt;<br>
<br>
::the wolf continued to laugh in his face before turining, her tail erect to clearly show she was not going to submit, but it was not so high that it meant challenge:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 166<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/16/01 7:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Bring it on</span><hr size=1> Dymastar looked onto Anya and laughed. &quot;You think, that a measly woman can defeat me? Oh how little do you know. I am the strongest and the fastest in the world. How can one pathetic woman stop me?&quot; He glared into the wolf's eyes. &quot;Bring...her...on.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usheyala.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sheyala</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 261<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/17/01 9:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://geocities.com/Tokyo/Pagoda/8446/mononoke_poster.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hope</span><hr size=1> ::Anya turned back once to glare at him::<br>
<br>
&quot;I wouldn't say that Dymaster... You might make her very angry....  At any rate I must take my leave of you.  There are things to be done and people to see&quot;<br>
<br>
::She smirked once more and disappeared into the forest,  She had stalled him enough.  Sheyala was coming.  Now it was time for Anya to take Shey's place to watch the war.  Obviously Shey was being ignored by Ares.  And it was HER turn to draw attention.:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 168<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/17/01 9:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> what sort of battle persues?</span><hr size=1> What was once Mamartigan stayed where he was now, no walking in unknown destinations. Just standing and waiting. Waiting for his adversary to come. He stood motionless, except for his hair blowing in the wind. Dymastar looked on and wondered, could this Sheyala realy defeat this body? It didnt seem possible. But there was something inside of him that told him that he would fight with more than just Sheyala in this battle. Something also told him that he may even loose. Thunder rolled through the blackening sky, as Dymastar waited. Waited for his adversary. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usheyala.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sheyala</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 264<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/17/01 9:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://geocities.com/Tokyo/Pagoda/8446/mononoke_poster.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Revenge from her past</span><hr size=1> ::Fianlly Sheyala arrived at the last destroyed village and knew the man standing where he was.  She dismounted slowly and whacked her horse on the rump, making it run far away so that it wouldn't be hurt.   Shey knew this would be a long hard battle.  She also knew that it meant everything to her.::<br>
<br>
&quot;So you are the one I sensed from so far away.  hmpf I warned Madmartigan not to cross me... But that was directed towards you... Dymaster.&quot;<br>
<br>
::She took a defensive stance knowing what was coming.  she dug her feet into the ground, dirt piling on either side of her boots.  Her braid had come loose during her furious ride so all that held her unruly hair backwas a small leather thong rope that ran around her forehead-and that barely seemed to help.::<br>
<br>
&quot;Now leave my friend be or I will beat you senseless&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 169<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/18/01 11:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hence is he gone?</span><hr size=1> Dymastar looks at shey menicingly for a minute then breaks out laughing. &quot;Your friend is screaming inside his body. He begs for me to let him go, but he begs me even more not to harm you. You seem to be the only friend he has, and thus cares for you a lot. Everyone elce is either a battle comrad or an enemy...or dead. Its a pitty though, i'll have to kill his only friend if she gets in my way. And your in my way. Now, you must die.&quot; Dymastar said himself to be in full controle of Madmartigan's body, although something on his face seemed that he wasnt, but he proceded anyway. With the speed of lightning, Dymastar had drawn his iron sword, and was slashing fast at Sheyala's head. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usheyala.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sheyala</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 265<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/18/01 1:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://geocities.com/Tokyo/Pagoda/8446/mononoke_poster.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Thirst for bloodshed</span><hr size=1> ::Sheyala smirked, her canine's seeming longer than usual, protruding from her mouth as she simpered and jumped aside, dodging the blade with ease.::<br>
<br>
&quot;Funny, you think I hesitate to kill you.  I know that if you don't come out willingly I have to kill your shell first.  I will not hesitate-will not flinch.  For destroying you and setting Madmartigan free anyway I can is all that matters.&quot;<br>
